OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497486
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FA 'Screens Away, Time to Play'
OL,7,Fcampaign has been launched in Guernsey
OL,8,Fwhich aims to raise healthier
OL,9,Fyoungsters.
OL,11,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO)
OL,12,Fhas issued guidance suggesting that
OL,13,Ftoo much screen time can negatively
OL,14,Fimpact children's brain development
OL,15,Fduring the first five years of their
OL,16,Flives.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497486
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FIf young children spend too much time
OL,7,Fon handheld devices, it can affect
OL,8,Ftheir attention, sleep, eyesight,
OL,9,Femotional regulation and overall
OL,10,Fwellbeing.
OL,12,FThe new campaign aims to streamline
OL,13,Fthis guidance, by suggesting low-cost
OL,14,Falternatives to screen time.
OL,16,FThese include: matching socks from the
OL,17,Flaundry basket, building blanket
OL,18,Fforts, hosting kitchen disco dance
OL,19,Fparties, or helping to set the table.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497486
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FAlex Hawkins-Drew, Guernsey's Director
OL,7,Fof Public Health, said: "The first
OL,8,F1001 days of a baby's life are really
OL,9,Fcritical for brain development.
OL,11,F"They need face-to-face contact with
OL,12,Fthe social world, either through a
OL,13,Fparent or carer.
OL,15,F"When they engage with screens,
OL,16,Fthey're getting much more limited
OL,17,Fcontact, and their development doesn't
OL,18,Fhappen as it should."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497486
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FThe WHO advises that babies up to the
OL,7,Fage of two should not use handheld
OL,8,Fdevices at all, except for family
OL,9,Fvideo calls.
OL,11,FThe guidance also recommends children
OL,12,Faged between two and five use these
OL,13,Fdevices for just one hour a day,
OL,14,Fideally split up into smaller chunks.
OL,16,FRuth Sharp, Head of Guernsey's Early
OL,17,FYears. said: "This is not about
OL,18,Fdemonising digital technology - it's
OL,19,Fabout moderation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497487
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FShe added: "Parenting, or being a
OL,7,Fcarer, is the hardest job in the world
OL,8,Fas we know.
OL,10,F"We don't want to make anyone feel
OL,11,Fguilty for their choices; we just want
OL,12,Fto arm parents with the right
OL,13,Finformation.
OL,15,FThe WHO guidance goes beyond an
OL,16,Fabsence of screens, and instead
OL,17,Fencourages physically active playtime.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
