OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773497487
OL,3,CCampaign launched to keep young
OL,4,Cchildren off screens
OL,6,FFor example, they suggest that
OL,7,Fchildren aged between 3-4 should be
OL,8,Fphysically active for at least three
OL,9,Fhours per day.
OL,11,F"What we really need to do is bring
OL,12,Fback play for children," said Dr Juana
OL,13,FWillumsen, WHO focal point for
OL,14,Fchildhood obesity and physical
OL,15,Factivity.
OL,17,F"This is about making the shift from
OL,18,Fsedentary time to playtime, while
OL,19,Fprotecting sleep. "
